title: Landing Page JS
description: A website of the Juana Sotelo agency to enroll in its micropigmentation courses.
description2: This project is a landing page I designed for my mother Juana Sotelo's company, which specializes in micropigmentation. As I am passionate about technology and the web, I decided to create a landing page to make it easier for potential clients to sign up for her micropigmentation courses. The landing page I designed is easy to access and navigate, and clearly presents all the necessary information so that interested individuals can make an informed decision about enrolling in the courses.
